  "optimization_hints": [
    "Q1: Heavily CPU-bound aggregation on 60M rows. Use partial aggregation + parallel hash agg. Target ~20K rows to GROUP BY stage.",
    "Q3: Multi-table join with selective date filters. Use bloom filter on filtered orders before probing lineitem. Order: customer → orders (low selectivity) → lineitem.",
